<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634110196557339298" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634118491675206183">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Click on <em>CheckBox </em>and the label indicates <em>Cheked </em>state of the <em>CheckBox </em>with message 'CheckBox state is &lt;CheckState  property value&gt;!'</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement3"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>CheckBox </em>contains the <em>CheckState </em>property and <em>CheckStateChange </em>event for manipulating with its checked state. The <em>CheckState </em>property defines current checked state of the <em>CheckBox</em>. The property can be contains the following values:<br /><strong>Unchecked </strong>&ndash; defines unchecked state of the <em>CheckBox </em>control<br /><strong>Checked </strong>&ndash; defines checked state of the <em>CheckBox </em>control<br /><strong>Indeterminate </strong>&ndash; defines indeterminate state of the <em>CheckBox </em>control. The state is accessed if <em>ThreeState </em>property is enabled for <em>CheckBox</em>.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2" />
  </Nodes>
</Data>
